doctype html
html
  head
    title NYCDB - Meet The Staff
    link(rel='icon', href='./images/favicon.ico', type='image/x-icon')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='./css/main.css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Ubuntu:400,700', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    link(href='https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Indie+Flower', rel='stylesheet', type='text/css')
    script(src='https://code.jquery.com/jquery-2.2.0.min.js')
    script(src='./js/nycdbFunctions.js')
  body
    #backgrounddiv
    #coverdiv
    // Header
    #header
      #logo
        a(href='./')
          img.logo(src='./images/nycdb_logo.svg')
      .mainmenu
        nav
          li
            a(href='./index') Home
          li
            a(href='./products') Our Beers
          li
            a(href='./staff') Our Staff
          li
            a(href='./about') About Us
          li
            a(href='./contact') Contact
    // Products
    #mainStaff
      #lindsey.staff
        #staffphoto1.staffphoto
          img(src='./images/staff/lindsey.jpg')
        .staffname
          | Lindsey Schaap
      #staffbox1.staffbox
        .staffboxphoto
          img(src='./images/staff/lindsey_big.jpg')
        .staffdescription
          span.subtitle Lindsey Schaap
          p
            | Lindsey is one of our co-founders and has strong expertise in everythign related to the brewing of beers. He's in charge of our brewery and also works on web development together with Thijs.
      #thijs.staff
        #staffphoto2.staffphoto
          img(src='./images/staff/thijs.jpg')
        .staffname
          | Thijs Tel
      #staffbox2.staffbox
        .staffboxphoto
          img(src='./images/staff/thijs_big.jpg')
        .staffdescription
          span.subtitle Thijs Tel
          p
            | Thijs is one of the co-founders of the NYCDB and is responsible for the quality control of all beers that leave our brewery. Together with Lindsey he is also in charge of web development and promotion.
    // Footer
    #footer
      .socialmedia
        a(href='http://www.facebook.com/NYCDB')
          img(src='./images/social/facebook.png')
        a(href='http://www.twitter.com/NYCDB')
          img(src='./images/social/twitter.png')
        a(href='http://www.deliveroo.nl')
          img(src='./images/social/deliveroo.png')
      #customerquotes
        #quote1.customerquote
          p.quote
            | The HTML beer is definitely one of the best pilsners I've ever tasted in my life!
          p.customername Zach Feldman
        #quote2.customerquote
          p.quote I love the way the jQuery ale comes with a sophisticated opening mechanism.
          p.customername Jon Miller
